  "body": "Was running a pod with an activeDeadlineSeconds on a 1.10 cluster.  The pod reached the deadline, but the pod status did *not* contain the latest state of the pod containers (pod containersStatus was empty).  The status only had the following fields:\r\n\r\n```\r\nstatus:\r\n  phase: Failed\r\n  reason: DeadlineExceeded\r\n  message: ...\r\n  startTime: ...\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe statuses were there immediately prior to the deadline being reached.\r\n\r\nThis broke API clients that were looking at container status.",
